{"tid":1172681,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)天眼救未來 美帝極黑暗","createTime":"2019-05-26T15:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T18:42:53.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b1da3847b4421b6f7441dabaff98f1fa3cc555","tid":1172681,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=c761cae7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=515e877e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=3c659ce3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original/d2i5Jusk6oFpNR34Syp281wnpsm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.tmdb.org%2Ft%2Fp%2Foriginal%2Fd2i5Jusk6oFpNR34Syp281wnpsm.jpg&h=04c1c6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c6/American_Made_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc6%2FAmerican_Made_Poster.jpg&h=0101c404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.克里斯&middot;強森擁有可以看見未來，並以行動改變未來的能力，不過擁有特殊能力的他，受不了政府和醫學機構的檢查，於是隱藏起來混在拉斯維加斯的小賭場賭博和變魔術維生。<br />\n不過此時有FBI幹員寇莉&middot;佛瑞斯前來找尋克里斯&middot;強森，原來為了要避免恐怖組織炸掉洛杉磯核能電廠的陰謀，佛瑞斯必須盡速找到強森並且改變這件可怕的未來。<br />\n<br />\n2.故事描述前TWA（美國航空前身）飛行員巴瑞&middot;塞爾專從事毒品走私，金盆洗手的他被CIA找上要求合作並提供情報。為此他開始協助DEA對付中南美洲新出現的共產主義威脅，這同時也成為了美國史上規模最大的秘密性行動之一<br />\n<br />\n11 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=22b087eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=9489fd56\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d126d7ded0a3fca4b79a64e7ac7a7f802d0e4b88","tid":1172681,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52808c17778b732b70f77210c6bd342520ddec1d","tid":1172681,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"h